{"type":"message","id":"25780b45","parentId":"7ff39eaf","timestamp":"2026-04-25T22:05:54.823Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bgoufopbfedz_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"DeanCompanion.xcodeproj\nDean_Companion.md\nResources\nSources\ndean companion\nforge.config.js\nindex.html\nlobster.jpg\nlobster_pixel_art.html\nnode_modules\nout\npackage-lock.json\npackage.json\nproject.yml\nsrc\nwebpack.main.config.js\nwebpack.renderer.config.js\nwebpack.rules.js"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":10,"aggregated":"DeanCompanion.xcodeproj\nDean_Companion.md\nResources\nSources\ndean companion\nforge.config.js\nindex.html\nlobster.jpg\nlobster_pixel_art.html\nnode_modules\nout\npackage-lock.json\npackage.json\nproject.yml\nsrc\nwebpack.main.config.js\nwebpack.renderer.config.js\nwebpack.rules.js","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-cody"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777154754823}}
{"type":"message","id":"fd05aa8e","parentId":"25780b45","timestamp":"2026-04-25T22:05:56.193Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me look at the route-assistant skill to understand the route camera setup.\n","thinkingSignature":"015fc39989983d80aaa7b09686b765bef08a765548f9c64d3e7a6ff3a8909365"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lgggjrawvyqb_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/skills/route-assistant/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":130,"output":59,"cacheRead":30080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30269,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777154754824,"responseId":"063c6dc243dcad22ede686956abcff73"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a633258e","parentId":"fd05aa8e","timestamp":"2026-04-25T22:05:56.203Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_lgggjrawvyqb_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: route-assistant\ndescription: Extract delivery/service route stops from screenshots and look up addresses by house number. Use when (1) user provides screenshots of route lists/manifests and asks to extract stops, (2) user sends a house number to look up a stop, or (3) user mentions route stops, delivery route, service route, or stop lookup.\n---\n\n# Route Assistant\n\nManages a route stop dataset built from screenshots. Two workflows.\n\n## Dataset Lookup Storage\n\nLocation: `~/.openclaw/skills/route-assistant/data/route_stops.json`\n\n**Data structure:**\n```json\n{\n  \"stops\": [\n    { \"stopNumber\": 1, \"fullAddress\": \"123 Main St, Knoxville, TN 37922\", \"houseNumber\": \"123\", \"packages\": 2 }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## Step 1: Extract from Screenshots\n\nWhen user provides screenshots of route lists/manifests:\n\n1. Use `image` tool to analyze ALL screenshots\n2. For each stop, extract:\n   - **Stop #** (or sequence number)\n   - **Full Address** (complete street address)\n   - **House Number** (the leading numeric part)\n   - **Package count** — count how many packages are listed for that stop (look for quantity labels, \"x2\", \"qty 2\", multiple entries, etc.)\n3. Build the dataset:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stops\": [\n    { \"stopNumber\": 1, \"fullAddress\": \"123 Main St, Knoxville, TN 37922\", \"houseNumber\": \"123\", \"packages\": 2 }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n4. Save to `~/.openclaw/skills/route-assistant/data/route_stops.json`\n5. Confirm: \"Got it — X stops extracted and stored.\"\n\n## Step 2: House Number Lookup\n\nWhen user sends a house number (e.g., \"456\" or \"123 Oak\"):\n1. Load `~/.openclaw/skills/route-assistant/data/route_stops.json`\n2. Search stops where `houseNumber` matches the input (exact string match)\n3. Return results using the rules below.\n\n### Return Rules\n\n**One match (1 package):**\n```\n[Full Address] — Stop #[X]\n```\n\n**One match (2+ packages):**\n```\n[Full Address] — Stop #[X] ⚠️ 2 PACKAGES\n```\n\n**Multiple matches:**\n```\nA. [Full Address] — Stop #[X] ⚠️ 2 PACKAGES\nB. [Full Address] — Stop #[X]\n```\n\n**No match:**\n```\nNo match found\n```\n\n### Critical Rules\n- **Never guess** — Only return verified matches from the dataset\n- **Never infer** — Do not fill in missing data\n- **Exact match only** — House number must match exactly as stored\n- **Always include** — Full address and stop number in every match\n- **Always flag multi-package stops** — When `packages >= 2`, always include the ⚠️ warning so Bobby catches it\n- **Empty dataset** — If no dataset exists, ask user to provide route screenshots first\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777154756203}}
{"type":"message","id":"d0bf6d49","parentId":"a633258e","timestamp":"2026-04-25T22:05:58.340Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check what cameraBobby has for route. The route camera mentioned in memory was \"Dean's Eye\" but I need to find out what's actually set up. Let me check the memory files and also check if there's a specific route camera setup.\n","thinkingSignature":"124d9a78841c840fe6457a93320aa8a96bd067b63dd3917d48af31c2d98be43b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b859rkrdrsof_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/skills/route-assistant/data/ 2>/dev/null || echo \"no data dir\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b859rkrdrsof_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/skills/route-assistant/data/route_stops.json 2>/dev/null || echo \"no stops file\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":779,"output":142,"cacheRead":30144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31065,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777154756203,"responseId":"063c6dc4d661e685f9a54dff0da027cf"}}
